rComments: Zoe was a great professor, she was very understanding and inspirational. Her readings were very relevant and exciting. The class was clear and it was alway's fresh and new content which she explained and made very accessible.

Zoe has exceptionally high expectations & she is indeed a tough grader. As a young professor, her insecurities about being a "legitimate professor whom students take seriously" is evident. The content was interesting but the assignments were arguably challenging. The TA was useless. I had to work really hard to get the grade I received in her class
